{
  "texts": [
    "Human resources (HR) is another domain that has been highly influenced by the introduction of AI systems.",
    "A recent study showed that approximately 45% of surveyed organizations use or plan to use AI algorithms to support their HR activities in the next five years (SHRM 2022).",
    "AI systems are used for hiring and firing processes, personalization of employees' social benefits, and identifying talents among many other instances (Chevalier 2022).",
    "Yet, literature suggests that people hold less favorable attitudes towards adopting AI technologies in the recruiting procedures and perceive AI recruiters as ineffective or less impartial than human interviewers (Acikgoz et al. 2020; Gonzalez et al. 2022; Zhang and Yencha 2022).",
    "The examples above demonstrate that jobs with high as well as low probability of automation scores are currently heavily influenced by the implementation of AI systems."
  ]
}